<HEADLINE> Poetry Recital in Memory of Deng Xiaoping in Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 8 (Xinhua) -- A music recital to honor the
contributions of the late Chinese leader Deng Xiaoping was held in
the Chinese capital today.
</P>
<P>
Hu Jintao, member of the Standing Committee of the Political
Bureau of the Central Committee of the Chinese Communist Party
(CPC), and Ding Guangen, member of the Secretariat of the Central
Committee of the CPC, and members of Deng's family attended the
