<HEADLINE> Moi to Visit Zambia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, April 8 (Xinhua) -- Kenyan President Daniel arap Moi
will leave here tomorrow for a three-day official visit to Zambia
where he will attend the COMESA heads of state and government
summit, the Kenya News Agency reported today.
</P>
