<HEADLINE> Iran Claims Five Iranians Held in Israel </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, April 9 (Xinhua) -- Iran claimed here today that five
Iranian nationals were held in Israel including two diplomats,
one cameraman, one driver and one clergyman.
</P>
<P>
