<HEADLINE> Chinese, Russian Enterprises Set Up Joint Venture </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UFA, Russia, April 9 (Xinhua) -- Two enterprises of China and
Russia signed an agreement today to set up a joint venture in Ufa,
capital of the Russian Republic of Baskirskaja.
</P>
<P>
