most powerful telecommunications companies in China.
</P>
<P>
The Beto Concern is one of the two largest communications
equipment producers in Russia.
</P>
<P>
The Huawei-Beto joint company, which is the first of its kind
set up by Huawei in Russia, is expected to produce high-quality
communication equipment able to compete in the world market.
</P>
<P>
Ren Zhengfei, president of the Huawei Company, said that his
company will establish another four joint ventures in Russia.
