<HEADLINE> Xinhua World News Summary at 7:30 GMT, April 9 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI -- Visiting Pakistan Foreign Minister Gohar Ayub Khan
Wednesday held an informal meeting with his Indian counterpart
I.K. Gujral and both sides decided to continue the dialogue.
</P>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS -- China, France, Russia, Britain and the United
States Tuesday reiterated their "strong and continuing support"
for the Nuclear Non-proliferation Treaty (NPT).
</P>
<P>
PARIS -- The first batch of French troops left France Tuesday
for Albania to join the multinational protection force for the
crisis-hit country, said military sources.
</P>
<P>
ROME -- Italy Tuesday reiterated its support for Poland's bid
to join the North Atlantic Treaty Organization (NATO) after two
days of talks cleared a misunderstanding between Rome and Warsaw.
