<HEADLINE> WB provides Aid For Conservation In Sri Lanka </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, April 9 (Xinhua) -- The World Bank will provide 14.8
million US dollars for Sri Lanka to help strengthen its
institutional and policy framework for environmental management
and conservation, according to World Bank sources here today.
