NYSE's composite index rose 1.63 to 402.31; and the American Stock
Exchange composite index rose 0.98 to 561.42.
</P>
<P>
The Nasdaq composite index, which by last Wednesday had slid
13.5 percent from its January high, rose 6.02 to 1,257.37.
